{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Star Chef Simulator, where your dream of running your own restaurant is about to become a reality! Immerse yourself in the exciting world of culinary entrepreneurship as you build and manage your restaurant from the ground up.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash your inner chef and dive in the art of cooking with 9 delicious dishes from around the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956720/extras/Dishes_1280x256.png?t=1738182936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cook with a variety of different ingredients, techniques and recipes to create culinary masterpieces that will delight your customers. Use various kitchen appliances such as the deep fryer, oven, stove or mixer and create unique dishes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956720/extras/Tools_Collage.png?t=1738182936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose Career Mode and unlock new content as you progress, or choose Sandbox Mode. This is where you can let your creativity run wild and focus on cooking without worrying about money or business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hire and manage your employees to keep your restaurant running smoothly. Build a strong team to handle the hustle and bustle of a busy kitchen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956720/extras/Worker_Collage.png?t=1738182936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your restaurant, from the walls to the floors, from the decor to the equipment. Create a unique dining experience and watch customers flock to your establishment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956720/extras/Customization.png?t=1738182936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep an eye on your finances as you make decisions to grow your business. Provide top-notch service to your guests to earn rave reviews. Listen to feedback and strive to deliver a memorable dining experience that keeps guests coming back for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956720/extras/DishRating.png?t=1738182936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Are you ready to take the helm of your own restaurant and become the ultimate culinary star chef? The world of gastronomy awaits you!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956720/extras/BecomeYourOwnChef_Banner.png?t=1738182936\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Tutorial Finished","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2956720/32e426d158afc0ef85731b638e4fb7e1f5abcc1e.jpg"},{"name":"Fruit Salad","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2956720/d8876fe7dba23a5f5f60eccc2b3a5fd1cbdf21e0.jpg"},{"name":"Mixed Salad","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2956720/0461fbfc743054cd6cb6cfcfc771641775a143ad.jpg"},{"name":"Pork Steak Menu","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2956720/493831810f23db6a747d0e2c416067d7140766d2.jpg"},{"name":"Tomato Soup","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2956720/3aaab71d0e269e748bc06e7a09afa3cfc5d9042a.jpg"},{"name":"Caprese Salad","path":"https://cdn.akamai.s